         <abstract>
            <p>Lease evaluation models have tended to overlook the significant impact of the investment tax credit in the lease vs. buy decision. This paper examines three different alternatives for the treatment of the investment tax credit and explores the implications of these alternatives on the lease-buy decision.</p>
         </abstract>
